Global Multifunctional Food Ingredients Market, By Type (Emulsions and Flavours, Hydrocolloids, Fibres, Oat Extracts, Yeast Extracts, Bulking Agents, Others) Application (Bakery and Confectionery Products, Meat and Poultry, Dessert and Toppings, Dairy Products, Processed Food Products, Others) - Industry Trends and Forecast to 2030.

